      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases relevant to rotating machinery and non-Newtonian flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against Taylor-Couette benchmark and lid-driven cavity benchmark at Re = 1000. Published verification studies for the MRF rotating frame formulation reviewed and confirmed applicable. Code verification requirements at level 2 satisfied."
    },
    {
