      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used in validation must be characterized and representative of the blood analogue used in CFD.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments used bovine blood at 30% hematocrit, consistent with CFD blood model parameterization. Sample characterization data available in published dataset. Level 1 requirements satisfied."
    },
