      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional and non-dimensional input parameters in CFD must match experimental conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Flow rates and rotational speeds matched to within 0.5% of experimental target values. Reynolds number and specific speed confirmed equivalent between CFD and experiment. Equivalency of input parameters at level 1 confirmed."
